    <PackageReleaseNotes>
      
      - Restructured the project to be more coherent.
      - Consolidated other projects into this one after generalizing the implementation.
      
      Added 
      
      - MappingExtension.CreateMapperConfigs
      - DIExtension.CreateDIConfigs
      - IAppSettingsExtensions
      - Wlvyr.Common.Reflection
