      - All previously existing interfaces are now in Wlvyr.Common.Configuration namespace.
      - Removed `BootstrapConfiguration`, repalced with `DIBootstrapConfiguration`
        - DIBootstrap uses this.
      - BaseAppSettings environment property changed.

    </PackageReleaseNotes>
  </PropertyGroup>

